.TH UTILITYKIT 1 "July 2026" "UtilityKit v5.10.6" "UtilityKit Tools"
.SH NAME
utility-ssh_tunnel \- Create, list, kill, and restart SSH port-forwards.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B utility ssh_tunnel
[\fIoptions\fP]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Create, list, kill, and restart SSH port-forwards.
.SH USAGE
.PP
.EX
tunnel create server.com:3000 --local 3000 --user deploy --name api
tunnel list
tunnel list --json
tunnel kill 1
tunnel restart api
.EE
.PP
.SH OPTIONS
.PP
Flag   |   Meaning
\fC--local PORT\fP   |   Local port (default: same as remote)
\fC--user USER\fP   |   SSH user
\fC--key FILE\fP   |   SSH identity file
\fC--autossh\fP   |   Auto-restart with autossh
\fC--name NAME\fP   |   Tunnel name for management
\fC--json\fP   |   Machine-readable list output
.PP
Config: \fC${XDG_CONFIG_HOME:-~/.config}/utilitykit/tunnels.conf\fP
